downloadDescription: The Microsoft Tunnel Deployment Guide provides general guidance and the necessary configuration steps to deploy Microsoft Tunnel Gateway to provide Intune MDM-managed mobile devices access to on-premises resources.
detailsSection: The Microsoft Tunnel Deployment Guide provides general guidance and the necessary configuration steps to deploy Microsoft Tunnel Gateway for the purpose of providing Intune MDM-managed mobile devices access to on-premises resources. The guide can be used for a lab or as a means of getting started in a production environment. The download also includes a networking insights reference with additional details.
